        }
      }
    },
    "Built with a privacy-first approach, Codelume runs inside the macOS sandbox and does not collect personal data. It is open source, transparent, and built for long-term reliability." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜秉持隐私优先原则，运行于 macOS 沙盒环境内，不收集个人数据。应用开源透明，并以长期稳定可靠为目标构建。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
