    },
    "Codelume" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume focuses on the playback engine and desktop integration. You can use your own compatible video wallpapers, and we encourage proper licensing and respect for original creators." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜专注于播放引擎与桌面集成能力。你可以使用自己的兼容视频壁纸，我们鼓励遵守授权规范并尊重原创作者。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume focuses on the playback engine—we don't create wallpaper content. Wallpaper quality determines the ceiling of the entire experience. If you have original wallpapers, you can submit them via email for other users to purchase. Pricing is decided by the original creator. Codelume takes a small share to cover server maintenance and development; the rest goes to the creator. Of course, there will always be free wallpapers available." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜专注于播放引擎的开发，不涉及壁纸内容创作。壁纸质量决定了动态壁纸体验的上限。如果你有优质的原创壁纸，可以通过邮箱投递，供其他用户购买使用。价格由原创作者决定。码镜仅收取少部分费用用于服务器维护与日常开发，其余部分结算给原创作者。当然，也会提供大量免费壁纸供大家使用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume is a dynamic wallpaper application designed exclusively for macOS, featuring a sleek design with comprehensive functionality. As a menu bar application, please remember to launch and use it from the menu bar—it won't be visible in your Dock." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜是一款专为 macOS 设计的动态壁纸，界面简洁，功能全面。它是一款菜单栏应用，请从菜单栏中启动并使用，不会显示在程序坞中。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume is a native macOS dynamic wallpaper app designed for smooth playback, low resource usage, and a polished desktop experience." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜是一款原生 macOS 动态壁纸应用，专注于流畅播放、低资源占用和精致的桌面体验。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume is a native, open-source dynamic wallpaper application built exclusively for macOS." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜是一款原生开源动态壁纸应用，专为 macOS 系统设计。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume is Running" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜正在运行中"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume offers a dedicated screen saver module that allows users to set their current dynamic wallpapers as screen savers after downloading and installing it. This creates a seamless visual transition between active desktop environments and idle states, extending dynamic aesthetics throughout the entire device usage cycle while ensuring privacy security and maintaining a consistent immersive visual experience." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "为此码镜提供了专属的屏幕保护程序模块，用户下载安装后即可将正在使用的动态壁纸设置为屏幕保护程序，实现桌面环境与休息状态的无缝视觉衔接，让动态美学贯穿设备使用的全周期，在保护隐私安全的同时营造始终如一的沉浸式视觉体验。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Codelume Screen Saver" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "码镜屏保"
